title: Cut the Rope
author: Mush-Co
description:
The world of Cut the Rope is finally in Minecraft! Help Om Nom collect all the candy by cutting the right ropes and using various gadgets in this physics-based puzzle adventure. 

Features:
- 100+ Unique levels
- Custom physics-based rope mechanics
- Playable Om Nom character
- 5 Different themed chapters
- Challenging boss levels
